Akwa Ibom State has been acknowledged as the best-performing state under the South-South region during the 2019 fiscal year by the World Bank Project Implementation. <img class="size-full wp-image-1263320 aligncenter" src="https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/3324dde5-8b1b-495e-9420-e3533cef93ef.jpg?resize=640%2C480&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="640" height="480" srcset="https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/3324dde5-8b1b-495e-9420-e3533cef93ef.jpg?w=960&amp;ssl=1 960w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/3324dde5-8b1b-495e-9420-e3533cef93ef.jpg?resize=300%2C225&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/3324dde5-8b1b-495e-9420-e3533cef93ef.jpg?resize=768%2C576&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/3324dde5-8b1b-495e-9420-e3533cef93ef.jpg?resize=58%2C44&amp;ssl=1 58w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/3324dde5-8b1b-495e-9420-e3533cef93ef.jpg?resize=260%2C194&amp;ssl=1 260w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/3324dde5-8b1b-495e-9420-e3533cef93ef.jpg?resize=173%2C130&amp;ssl=1 173w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/3324dde5-8b1b-495e-9420-e3533cef93ef.jpg?resize=560%2C420&amp;ssl=1 560w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" data-recalc-dims="1" /> The World Bank Country Director for Nigeria, Africa Region, Rachid Banmessaoud made this known in a Commendable Performance letter addressed to the state government. Banmessaoud congratulated the Akwa Ibom State government for also being recognised by World Bank Task Team Leaders on its performance in project implementation. He commended the commitment of Governor Udom Emmanuel led administration to cross the state, which according to him earned it the award. “This is to appreciate your state’s participation in the just concluded Nigeria Portfolio Performance Awards ceremony hosted by the World Bank Country Office in Abuja and to congratulate you on your states’ commendable performance which led to winning the first position, as the best performing state under the South-South Region. “The event recognised the performance of project implementation teams across the states and Federal institutions. “Through this event and award, we also believe Akwa Ibom State will significantly improve the overall momentum in the implementations of projects in the State” Banmessaoud added. Vanguard By Shina Abubakar Osun State has emerged the best-performing state in Nigeria in World Bank Project Implementation. The state also emerged the best among the participating states in the country in the Rural Access and Mobility Project 2 (RAMP 2) implementation. This was disclosed by the World Bank Country Director… September 15, 2019 In "News" By Chioma Onuegbu The World Bank has partnered Akwa Ibom state Agency for Community and Social Development Projects CSDP to execute 30 life- touching projects in ten communities across the state. National Coordinator Federal Project Support Units (FPSU), Dr Abdulkareem Obaje disclosed this yesterday in Uyo during a one-day training… September 30, 2019 In "Business" President Muhammadu Buhari says construction of section 5 of the East-West road from Oron (Akwa Ibom) to Calabar (Cross Rivers) to be funded under the forum on China-Africa cooperation has been approved. September 17, 2018 In "News"